  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个广播任务的状态流转图。核心场景是：管理员创建广播后，根据触发时间不同，有的要立即进入预计算，有的先挂起等待。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING",
        "Admin creates broadcast"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那\"挂起等待\"就是SCHEDULED状态，\"预计算\"是PREPARING。这两个都应该是从初始状态出发的分支对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。区分条件是： distant future 走SCHEDULED，immediate 或者 scheduled for near future 直接进PREPARING。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING",
        "Admin creates immediate broadcast",
        "scheduled for near future"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我画好了起点分支。那SCHEDULED之后怎么流转？需要有个调度器来触发吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "Pre-computation scheduler runs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Pre-computation scheduler runs 会把SCHEDULED推进到PREPARING。另外管理员随时能取消，SCHEDULED和PREPARING都要能到CANCELLED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING",
        "CANCELLED",
        "Admin cancels"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "PREPARING阶段在做异步用户拉取，成功就到READY，失败就到FAILED？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PREPARING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED",
        "Async user fetch succeeds",
        "Async user fetch fails"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。READY之后等Activation scheduler运行，也就是scheduled time arrives，进入ACTIVE真正发广播。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "ACTIVE",
        "Activation scheduler runs",
        "scheduled time arrives"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ACTIVE之后呢？正常结束应该是EXPIRED？还有别的终止路径吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACTIVE",
        "EXPIRED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ACTIVE有三种出口：Expiration scheduler运行后正常结束到EXPIRED；管理员通过API取消到CANCELLED；还有一种特殊情况——如果是group broadcast，DLT事件被消费后走到FAILED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ACTIVE",
        "EXPIRED",
        "CANCELLED",
        "FAILED",
        "Expiration scheduler runs",
